Subject: Re: [T2] 1600 CHT Question - Fan Blocking

Snoopy,

Top and bottom out of almost any canned food can.

Smooth off the edges, hold them together and drill a hole thru the middle
and then but them in with a bolt and nut.  Paint black first.

Easily removable later and if painted, hardly noticeable.

Cheers, dave

